### Get all incidents
GET http://localhost:8000/api/incidents
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a new incident (example pothole)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/incidents
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Big pothole near crossing",
  "lat": 22.56,
  "lng": 88.39,
  "photoUrl": "https://placehold.co/200x200.png"
}

###

### Update incident status (mark resolved)
PATCH http://localhost:8000/api/incidents/{{incident_id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "resolved",
  "assignedTo": "Officer-101"
}

###

### Get traffic prediction
GET http://localhost:8000/api/predict?type=traffic
Accept: application/json

###

### Get waste overflow prediction
GET http://localhost:8000/api/predict?type=waste
Accept: application/json
